    {
      "id": "field-driven-class-artifacts-contract-spec",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Shared Field Address Grammar",
      "position": {
        "x": 1420,
        "y": 540
      },
      "width": 620,
      "height": 760,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Shared Field Address Grammar v0\n\n## Artifact level\nThese stay on the graph authority surface and identify or frame the artifact itself.\n\n- `identity.graphId`\n- `identity.name`\n- `identity.version`\n- `identity.description`\n- `intent.kind`\n- `intent.scope`\n- authorship / authority / timestamps\n\nRule: if it identifies the graph artifact or explains how the system should treat the whole artifact, it stays at artifact level.\n\n## Field level\nThese are addressed functional values that the runtime, editor, bridge, or validator should be able to read directly.\n\n### Shared class fields\n- `class.key`\n- `class.label`\n- `class.meaning`\n- `class.version`\n- `class.source`\n- `render.stroke`\n- `render.width`\n- `render.dash`\n- `render.routingHint`\n- `render.labelTone`\n- `compat.sourceKinds`\n- `compat.targetKinds`\n- `validation.requiredDataKeys`\n- `validation.rules`\n- `validation.onError`\n\n### Node-class leaning fields\n- `node.defaultLabel`\n- `node.defaultWidth`\n- `node.defaultHeight`\n- `node.defaultColor`\n- `node.defaultData`\n- `node.defaultPorts`\n- `node.dataSchema`\n- `node.allowLabel`\n- `node.allowSize`\n- `node.allowColor`\n- `node.allowPorts`\n- `node.allowData`\n- `node.dataMode`\n\n### Edge-class leaning fields\n- `edge.defaultEdgeType`\n- `edge.legendRole`\n- `edge.semanticAuthority`\n\n## Doctrine\n- `field` nodes are the canonical semantic contract surface.\n- `markdown` explains the contract to humans.\n- `manifest` may be read only as temporary migration compatibility.\n- `legend` is never semantic authority.\n\n## Next move\nUse this exact path table to migrate one canonical node class and one canonical edge class, then tighten the loaders around these paths.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "identity": {
